# Development Goals

The long-term objective of SentinelGRC is to provide a modular, extensible, and vendor-neutral platform capable of supporting technical evidence collection and compliance reporting across multiple regulatory frameworks. Every architectural decision should favor maintainability, transparency, portability, and reuse over framework-specific implementations.
